
h3 Title Control

.row
	.col-md-6
		.form-group
			label Replace Pattern
			input.form-control(
				type='text',
				[(ngModel)]='config.store.titleControl.replacePattern',
				(ngModelChange)='config.save()',
			)
			p Replaces the title with a new value entirely. The escape sequences listed can be used to insert metadata into the new title.
	.col-md-3
		dl
			dt \t
			dd The original, unprocessed title
			dt \i
			dd The tab ID (internal)
			dt \scmd
			dd The shell command (ie. powershell.exe)
			dt \sname
			dd The shell name (ie. Windows Powershell)
	.col-md-3
		dl
			dt \spid
			dd The shell PID
			dt \pid
			dd The PID of the child process
			dt \cmd
			dd The command of the child process (ie. node.exe)
			dt \cwd
			dd The current working directory of the terminal

